n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n1. **错误模式**：所有错误都来自frontend服务，主要涉及两类RPC调用失败：\n   - 获取产品推荐服务失败（recommendationservice）\n   - 获取货币信息失败（currencyservice）\n\n2. **关键发现**：\n   - 错误类型主要为`context canceled`和`transport is closing`，表明连接被主动取消或传输层关闭\n   - 故障影响多个节点（aiops-k8s-03、04、07）上的frontend实例\n   - 故障时间跨度从16:11到16:25，持续约14分钟\n\n3. **根因推测**：下游服务recommendationservice和currencyservice可能出现了可用性问题，导致frontend服务的RPC调用超时或被取消。", "raw_trace_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载trace数据。UUID: 10889e22-221，共 20 个异常组合，10 个状态组合", "filtered_traces": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,normal_avg_duration,anomaly_avg_duration,anomaly_count\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations,124078.63908275458,56638902.590666674,出现次数:25\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations,142454.26842872082,56756873.848000005,出现次数:25\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.RecommendationService/ListRecommendations,118341.52217149167,56842343.8125,出现次数:24\naiops-k8s-06,productcatalogservice,frontend-0,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,9974.589102963795,12442.666666666666,出现次数:10\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,11371.846083869175,14581.555555555555,出现次数:9\naiops-k8s-06,productcatalogservice,frontend-1,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,9948.04346414364,12427.305555555555,出现次数:9\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,11203.635050935625,14851.722222222223,出现次数:9\naiops-k8s-06,productcatalogservice,frontend-2,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,9988.595232546208,12483.857142857143,出现次数:7\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,11480.30423854856,15817.785714285714,出现次数:7\naiops-k8s-01,recommendationservice,recommen